---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-28 pb-20">
    <h1 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#555] space-y-4">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 22, 2026</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mt-8">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>Thalux AI collects information necessary to provide our services: business contact details, phone numbers for call routing, website analytics data, and payment information processed through our secure payment provider, Stripe.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mt-8">2. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>We use collected information to deliver and maintain our services, process payments, communicate with clients about their accounts, and improve our service offerings.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mt-8">3. Payment Processing</h2>
      <p>All payment processing is handled by Stripe, Inc. We do not store credit card numbers or banking information on our servers. Payment data is transmitted directly to Stripe using industry-standard encryption.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mt-8">4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain business records and account information for the duration of our engagement and as required by applicable tax and record-keeping laws.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mt-8">5. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related inquiries: <a href="tel:+171****0566" class="text-[#E5B73C]">(717) 537-0566</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>